<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>V2A Inspect — Experiment Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background: #f8f9fa; color: #212529; line-height: 1.5; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 24px 0 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6; padding-bottom: 6px; }
        h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 16px 0 8px; }
        .meta { color: #6c757d; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .meta span { margin-right: 16px; }

        /* Navigation */
        nav { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        nav a { color: #0d6efd; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 16px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        nav a.active { font-weight: 700; color: #212529; }

        /* Cards */
        .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .card-header { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }

        /* Tables */
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 8px 0; }
        th, td { padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
        th { background: #f1f3f5; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
        .best { background: #d4edda; }
        .worst { background: #f8d7da; }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">

        <h1>V2A Inspect 실험 리포트 (4-Track Pipeline)</h1>
        <div class="meta">
            <span>🎬 {{ stats|length }}개 영상</span>
            <span>⚙️ 4-Track Pipeline</span>
        </div>

        <nav>
            <a href="index.html" class="active">대시보드</a>
            {% for s in stats %}
            <a href="per_video/{{ s.video_id }}.html">{{ s.video_id }}</a>
            {% endfor %}
        </nav>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">📊 4-Track 분석 요약</div>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>항목</th>
                    <th>Scenes (avg)</th>
                    <th>Tracks (avg)</th>
                    <th>Groups (avg)</th>
                </tr>

                <tr>
                    <td><strong>현재 분석 (All Videos)</strong></td>
                    <td>{{ avg_scenes }}</td>
                    <td>{{ avg_tracks }}</td>
                    <td>{{ avg_groups }}</td>
                </tr>

            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">🎬 영상별 상세</div>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <th>영상 ID</th>
                    <th>길이</th>
                    <th>씬 수</th>
                    <th>트랙 수</th>
                    <th>그룹 수</th>
                    <th>링크</th>
                </tr>
                
                {% for s in stats %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ s.video_id }}</td>
                    <td>{{ s.total_duration }}s</td>
                    <td>{{ s.num_scenes }}</td>
                    <td>{{ s.num_tracks }}</td>
                    <td>{{ s.num_groups }}</td>
                    <td><a href="per_video/{{ s.video_id }}.html">상세 보기 →</a></td>
                </tr>
                {% endfor %}

            </table>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>
